<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٦٠٢ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو الْيَمَانِ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا شُعَيْبٌ، عَنِ الزُّهْرِيِّ بِهَذَا،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(مَا أَدْرِي<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗٢٥٧١⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مَا يُفْعَلُ بِهِ).<span class="c5"> قَالَتْ:</span> وَأَحْزَنَنِي فَنِمْتُ، فَرَأَيْتُ لِعُثْمَانَ عَيْنًا تَجْرِي،<span class="c5"> فَأَخْبَرْتُ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(ذَلِكَ عَمَلُهُ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
